### What are you passionate about, Tico? 
- I love 🤩[solving problems](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/How_to_Solve_It "Polyas") 🤔🧩, but I love 🥰*__PEOPLE__* 👥 more!

### Why do you love 'people' so much? 
- Well, because ☝🏻God loved me [FIRST](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=k2iHNzNJkJw "FIRST")🙏🏻 & because He gave me an [ENFJ-T](https://www.16personalities.com/enfj-personality "Protagonist") personality type 😅.

### Why do you love 'solving problems' then?
- __*ALL*__ 'problems' affect *__REAL__* people 😞, so *solving* them is just ☝🏻one way that I [help](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zcruIov45bI "Helping Others Video") 🤗others 🤷🏻‍♂️.

### What experience do you have solving problems?
- In the [PT clinic](https://res.cloudinary.com/tico-cloudinary/image/upload/v1565150347/Portfolio/therapy_pitmji.jpg "PT-Clinic") 🤕, in the [weight room](https://youtu.be/VMKQ6VuJBno "weight-room") 🏋🏻, at my [Church](https://www.linkedin.com/posts/elkton-missionary-church_jesus-god-elkton-activity-6554791593495322624-J0XW "EMC") ⛪, on the [court](https://youtu.be/1s9HIODLhio "dunk") ⛹🏻, at my [school](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=erWWTNtskSw "Queue-tutorial") 👨🏻‍🎓, & even [outside](https://youtu.be/boLvDmxVj4U "outside") 🏌🏻, but more recently, in my [code](https://youtu.be/masJin41ae8?t=154 "lambda-showcase") 💻.
